    "Under Detectron2, we utilize the Faster R-CNN + FPN algorithm and employ a pre-trained model.",
    "In Detectron2, there are no epochs, only iterations.",
    "However, the maximum number of iterations can be artificially set based on the size of the dataset.",
    "MMDetection is an open-source project initiated by SenseTime and the Chinese University of Hong Kong for object detection tasks.",
    "It implements a wide range of object detection algorithms based on PyTorch and encapsulates the processes of dataset construction, model building, training strategies, and other tasks into modules."
